title: Oceanic LoL 5v5 FINAL
body:
Starting at 7pm AEST tonight (QLD) we have the finals for our 5v5 Double Elimination competition.


After a full day of competition we will see 2 teams battle it out for a Triumphant Ryze skin and RP.

In the final so far we have:

He Needed Precisely 2 cards to win - They have been undefeated throughout the day.

In a battle for the 2nd spot in the final we have:

Le Toucan
&
Team Solid

These 2 teams are currently playing!

Come check it out for a chance to win some RP between games.

replies.body: Couldn't watch the full game of Team solid vs 2card2win. These team need lessons in strategy. OPL is much better class. Commentators were ok though.
